description: WHO ARE WE?  We are a rockin’ burger truck; Imagine Hard rock café on wheels, add in a couple of “Mix’D UP folks” blended finely with the best quality ingredients (purchased locally as well as renewable and friendly sources), dust heavy with love and you get the best burger and fries known to the human race!To get the inside scoop on Mix'D UP's Brett Eanes, check out the Roaming Hunger interview here: http://roaminghunger.com/blog/4264/featured-food-truck-mixd-up
name: MIX'd UP Burgers
